snippet.description: From industry news to techy trends to newsmaker interviews, no technology angle is too small or obsc

snippet.title: Circa News (Android)
snippet.description: Circa is a fantastic free tool for reading breaking news and staying informed wherever you are.

snippet.title: Bing News
snippet.description: A pleasing design and stable performance make Bing News a must-have free app to effortlessly keep up with the news.

snippet.title: Pixar goes back to the future to make 'Monsters University'
snippet.description: In the 12 years since "Monsters Inc." came out, Pixar has seen several tech advances that make the new "Monsters University" prequel a richer visual experience -- notice all the hairs on Sully and the hundreds of extra characters in the background. CNET'S Sumi Das goes behind the scenes at Pixar.

snippet.title: Facebook Paper
snippet.description: Facebook's Paper is a new and attractive way to browse the social network and get the latest news, but its unclear why it's better to have two Facebook apps rather than one.

snippet.title: Material for Android
snippet.description: Material could one day be a great, simpler alternative to Flipboard, but first it has to fix its performance issues.

snippet.title: Data breach at University of Maryland exposes 300K records
snippet.description: School president apologies for a "sophisticated" security breach that exposed the sensitive personal information faculty, staff, and students at the school since 1998.

snippet.title: Can a Silicon Valley startup solve state university woes?
snippet.description: San Jose State University is partnering with tech startup Udacity, which offers online computer science and mathematics courses. CNET's Sumi Das explains how the first-of-its-kind program could help students graduate faster and save money.

snippet.title: Top Chinese university linked to alleged military cybercrime unit
snippet.description: Reuters has turned up a research connection between Shanghai Jiaotong University and the People's Liberation Army unit suspected of participation in cyberattacks on the West.

snippet.title: Yahoo for Android
snippet.description: More than just a news app, Yahoo stands out for its customization and search tools.
